Enclosing class:
cGalaxy
public static enum cGalaxy.eGalaxyType extends Enum<cGalaxy.eGalaxyType>
Enumeration of galaxy types based on the Hubble classification system. Includes elliptical, lenticular, spiral, barred spiral, and irregular galaxy types.
